Filter to return only the ones where the answer is NO. impeach %>% filter(for_impeachment == "NO") %>% summarise(for_impeachment) ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` # A tibble: 26 x 1 for_impeachment 1 NO 2 NO 3 NO 4 NO 5 NO 6 NO 7 NO 8 NO 9 NO 10 NO #
